Message: Could you please tell us how we can replenish the balance to launch the tests? We have added a card, but we cannot pay the amount. Can you make us an invoice for 100 dollars? We will pay and start the tests.

It sounds like you're having trouble with your payment method. Unfortunately, we cannot create invoices for specific amounts like $100. However, you can add ad credits to your account using a credit card. If your card payment is failing, I recommend contacting your bank or trying a different payment method. For more details on billing and payments, you can check out our Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide). If you continue to experience issues, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
